      "term": "digital-trust-ecosystem",
      "commitHash": "00608bb6ce7f7e6285f202b580548d61ee716621",
      "content": "[[def: digital-trust-ecosystem, digital trust ecosystem, digital trust ecosystems]]\n\n~ A [[ref: digital ecosystem]] in which the participants are one or more interoperating [[ref: trust communities]]. Governance of the various [[ref: roles]] of [[ref: governed parties]] within a digital trust ecosystem (e.g., [[ref: issuers]], [[ref: holders]], [[ref: verifiers]], [[ref: certification bodies]], [[ref: auditors]]) is typically managed by a [[ref: governing body]] using a [[ref: governance framework]] as recommended in the [[ref: ToIP Governance Stack]]. Many digital trust ecosystems will also maintain one or more [[ref: trust lists]] and/or [[ref: trust registries]].\n"
